Class DefaultAssociativeLinkageSystem

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jactr.core.module.declarative.basic.DefaultAssociativeLinkageSystem
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IAssociativeLinkageSystem, IInstallable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    DefaultAssociativeLinkageSystem4

    public class DefaultAssociativeLinkageSystem
extends java.lang.Object
implements IAssociativeLinkageSystem
    creates Link4 links, but does not install any code to add/remove/learn the links

    harrison
